Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Satellite communication
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx7w
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 16 Jan 1983
The future of global communication via satellite - and the man who foresaw it all, Arthur C. Clarke. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less